      "type": "User",
      "site_admin": false,
      "name": null,
      "patch_url": null
    },
    "body": "The script harness was calling `GetSigOpCount`, `HasValidOps`, `IsPayToAnchor`, `IsPayToScriptHash`, `IsPayToWitnessScriptHash`, and `IsPushOnly` on the fuzzed CScript. All of these are already covered by the `script_ops` harness, which is the dedicated harness for CScript member methods. Also, add the missing `IsPayToAnchor` call to `script_ops` so the move preserves coverage.\r\n",
